    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/8fefbc38fab7883b145df1852c5a3767.poster.avif?t=1746731768\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/8fefbc38fab7883b145df1852c5a3767.webm?t=1746731768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/8fefbc38fab7883b145df1852c5a3767.mp4?t=1746731768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fist of Yokai</strong> is a roguelite dungeon crawler with an innovative hack and slash mechanic that will get you hooked. Inspired by modern <strong>Roguelites </strong>(Binding of Isaac, Hades, Neon Abyss, etc.) and frenetic <strong>Hack and Slash</strong> games (Devil May Cry, Bayonetta, etc.) adding our own personal twist. Hard to master mechanics, incredibly rewarding feeling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/4e4fe7baecb1ce5a1cabb28482a37859.poster.avif?t=1746731768\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/4e4fe7baecb1ce5a1cabb28482a37859.webm?t=1746731768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/4e4fe7baecb1ce5a1cabb28482a37859.mp4?t=1746731768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SAVE SHINCHOKU</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summoned by the CEO of Shinchoku’s most wealthy company, you’ll strap on your gauntlets and smash the invader yokai, exploring and cleaning the never repeating metropolis and saving their citizens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KILL THEIR LEADERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the power of your friendly Hitodama to face yokai leaders like Raiju, the thunder itself, in an epic, chaotic battle. Discover the reasons behind the invasion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/146bc7e67593f2772ff6e19f46b5121b.poster.avif?t=1746731768\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/146bc7e67593f2772ff6e19f46b5121b.webm?t=1746731768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/146bc7e67593f2772ff6e19f46b5121b.mp4?t=1746731768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BOOST UP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recover your strength in Kitsune's room and alter your fighting style by transitioning between a variety of abilities. Strive to improve continuously, transforming once-impossible challenges into effortless feats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/125169eeaae593cf09c0e294d118c5af.poster.avif?t=1746731768\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/125169eeaae593cf09c0e294d118c5af.webm?t=1746731768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381550/extras/125169eeaae593cf09c0e294d118c5af.mp4?t=1746731768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RogueSlash: Replayability of a rogue-lite with the intensity of Hack and Slash games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 120 rooms (and going up), tweaked by our best level designers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anime style art and VFXs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Innovative mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awesome soundtrack.</p></li></ul>",
